<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />Unless Yahweh had been my help,</para>

<para style="q1">I would soon be lying down in the place of silence.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />When I said, "My foot is slipping,"</para>

<para style="q1">Your covenant faithfulness, Yahweh, held me up.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />When cares within me are many, your consolations make me happy.</para>
